  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A sphere of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot radius from a point within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A target takes [[/r 12d6]] necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><p><strong>Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 2d6]] for each slot level above 6th.</p><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 9th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 9d6]]. This spell's total would damage be [[/r 25d6]] necrotic damage.</p>",
